---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about Natred's approach to honest IT services. 12 years of industry experience delivering transparent IT support in Johannesburg and across South Africa."
>
  <HeroSection
    title="An Honest IT Company"
    subtitle="Built on transparency, delivered with expertise"
    description="Natred was founded on a simple principle: IT companies shouldn't overcomplicate things to pad their invoices. We provide straightforward IT support with transparent pricing."
    compact={true}
    showCta={false}
  />

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-text">
          <div class="accent-line"></div>
          <h2 class="animate-on-scroll fade-up">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="animate-on-scroll fade-up">
            Natred was built on a simple observation: most IT companies make things more complicated
            than they need to be. Complex jargon, opaque invoices, unnecessary "solutions" that
            create new problems.
          </p>
          <p class="animate-on-scroll fade-up">
            Backed by over 12 years of combined industry experience across enterprise and SMB
            environments, our team understands what businesses actually need from their IT
            partner—and what they don't.
          </p>
          <p class="animate-on-scroll fade-up">
            Natred exists to be different. We give you straight answers, transparent pricing, and IT
            that actually works. When something needs to be fixed, we fix it. When you don't need
            something, we tell you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="content-visual animate-on-scroll fade-left">
          <div class="stat-block">
            <span class="stat-number">12+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years Industry Experience</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-block">
            <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Transparent Pricing</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-block">
            <span class="stat-number">0</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Hidden Fees</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="section section-charcoal">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll fade-up">The "Honest IT" Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="philosophy-grid stagger-children">
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="philosophy-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="8" y="16" width="48" height="32" rx="2" stroke="#f26722" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="28" x2="56" y2="28" stroke="#f26722" stroke-width="2"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="36" x2="32" y2="36" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="42" x2="28" y2="42" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="48" cy="40" r="6" fill="#f26722"/>
              <text x="48" y="43" font-size="8" fill="#fff" text-anchor="middle">R</text>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Itemized Invoices</h3>
          <p>Every line item explained. Every cost justified. You see exactly what you're paying for—hardware, software, labour, markup (if any). No "miscellaneous charges."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="philosophy-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="24" stroke="#f26722" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M 22 32 L 28 38 L 42 24" stroke="#f26722" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Honest Recommendations</h3>
          <p>If you don't need something, we'll tell you. We'd rather have a long-term client who trusts us than squeeze extra revenue from unnecessary services.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="philosophy-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="12" y="8" width="40" height="48" rx="2" stroke="#f26722" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
              <circle cx="32" cy="24" r="8" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M 20 48 Q 20 36 32 36 Q 44 36 44 48" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Plain Language</h3>
          <p>We explain things in terms you understand. No hiding behind jargon, no making simple things sound complicated to justify our existence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="philosophy-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M 32 8 L 56 20 L 56 44 L 32 56 L 8 44 L 8 20 Z" stroke="#f26722" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M 32 32 L 32 56" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2"/>
              <path d="M 32 32 L 56 20" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2"/>
              <path d="M 32 32 L 8 20" stroke="#888" stroke-width="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Know Our Limits</h3>
          <p>We don't pretend to do everything. If you need security systems, telecoms, or other specialized work, we partner with people who are actually experts in those areas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Legal Entity Section -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-info animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <h2>Company Information</h2>
        <div class="legal-grid">
          <div class="legal-item">
            <span class="legal-label">Trading Name</span>
            <span class="legal-value">Natred</span>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-item">
            <span class="legal-label">Legal Entity</span>
            <span class="legal-value">Avian Forge (Pty) Ltd</span>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-item">
            <span class="legal-label">Registration Number</span>
            <span class="legal-value">2024/212590/07</span>
          </div>
          <div class="legal-item">
            <span class="legal-label">Location</span>
            <span class="legal-value">Johannesburg, South Africa</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section section-charcoal cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content animate-on-scroll fade-up">
        <h2>Ready to Work With an Honest IT Company?</h2>
        <p>Get in touch for a free assessment. No obligation, no hard sell—just a straight conversation about your IT needs.</p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-open-contact-modal>Get In Touch</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .content-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .content-text p {
    color: var(--light-gray);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .content-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .stat-block {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    border: 1px solid var(--dark-gray);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 30px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .stat-block:hover {
    border-color: var(--natred-orange);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--natred-orange);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    display: block;
    color: var(--light-gray);
    font-size: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .philosophy-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .philosophy-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }

  .philosophy-item h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .philosophy-item p {
    color: var(--light-gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .legal-info {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .legal-info h2 {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .legal-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .legal-item {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--dark-gray);
  }

  .legal-label {
    display: block;
    color: var(--natred-orange);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .legal-value {
    display: block;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--dark-gray);
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: var(--light-gray);
    font-size: 18px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .philosophy-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .legal-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .content-visual {
      order: -1;
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .stat-block {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 140px;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 36px;
    }
  }
</style>
